\c 22
\s Ubungcwele beminikelo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono kuAroni lakumadodana akhe ukuthi bazehlukanise\x + Nani 6.3.\x* lezinto ezingcwele zabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Levi 22.3; Eks. 28.38; Dute. 15.19.\x*, bangangcolisi ibizo lami elingcwele\x + Levi 18.21.\x*; ngoba zingcwele kimi: NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 3 Tshono kibo \add uthi\add*: Loba nguwuphi umuntu ezizukulwaneni zenu owenzalo yenu yonke osondela ezintweni ezingcwele, abantwana bakoIsrayeli abazingcwelisela iN\nd kosi\nd*, nxa ukungcola kwakhe kuphezu kwakhe\x + 7.20.\x*, lowomuntu uzaqunywa asuke phambi kwami. NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 30.33.\x*\nd*.
\v 4 Ngulowo lalowo owenzalo kaAroni, ongumlephero, loba olokugobhoza, kangadli ezintweni ezingcwele aze ahlambuluke\x + 14.2; 15.13.\x*. Lothinta lakuphi okungcoliswe yisidumbu\x + Num. 19.11.\x*, kumbe indoda okuphuma kuyo ubudoda bokuhlangana\x + 15.16.\x*,
\v 5 kumbe loba ngubani othinta loba yiyiphi into ehuquzelayo, angcoliswa yiyo\x + 11.24,43,44.\x*, kumbe umuntu angcoliswa nguye, ngakho konke ukungcola kwakhe\x + 15.7,19.\x*,
\v 6 umuntu othinta lokhu uzakuba ngongcolileyo kuze kuhlwe, angadli okwezinto ezingcwele ngaphandle kokuthi ageze umzimba wakhe ngamanzi\x + 15.5-11; Heb. 10.22.\x*.
\v 7 Nxa selitshonile ilanga uzahlambuluka; lemva kwalokho angadla okwezinto ezingcwele, ngoba kuyikudla kwakhe\x + 21.17,22. Nani 18.11,13; Levi 3.11.\x*.
\v 8 Ingcuba lokudatshuliweyo kangakudli ukuzingcolisa ngakho. NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + 7.24.\x*\nd*.
\v 9 Ngakho bazagcina umlayo wami, ukuze bangathwali isono ngawo, bafele kuso, sebewungcolisile. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* ebangcwelisayo\x + 19.17; Eks. 28.43.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Njalo kakho owemzini ozakudla into engcwele. Ohlala lompristi loyisisebenzi esiqhatshiweyo kangadli into engcwele\x + 1 Sam. 21.6.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa uba umpristi ethenga umuntu eyintengo yemali yakhe, yena angadla okwayo, lozelwe emzini wakhe, bona bangadla okokudla kwakhe\x + Nani 18.11,13.\x*.
\v 12 Lendodakazi yompristi, uba isiba ngeyendoda yemzini, yona kayingadli okomnikelo wezinto ezingcwele\x + Nani 18.11,13.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa indodakazi yompristi, nxa ingumfelokazi loba ingelahliweyo ingelanzalo, isibuyele emzini kayise\x + Gen. 38.11. Ruthe 1.8.\x* njengebutsheni bayo, izakudla okokudla kukayise; kanti kakho owemzini ongadla kukho\x + 10.14. Nani 18.11,19.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Njalo nxa umuntu esidla into engcwele ngokungazi, uzakwengezelela kuyo ingxenye yesihlanu yayo, anike umpristi into engcwele\x + 4.2; 5.15,16,18.\x*.
\v 15 Njalo kabayikungcolisa izinto ezingcwele zabantwana bakoIsrayeli abaziphakamisela iN\nd kosi\x + Nani 18.32.\x*\nd*,
\v 16 babenze bathwale ububi becala, lapho besidla izinto zabo ezingcwele; ngoba ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* ebangcwelisayo\x + 22.9.\x*.
\p
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 18 Tshono kuAroni, lakumadodana akhe, lakubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli, uthi kubo: Ngulowo lalowo owendlu kaIsrayeli, lowabezizweni koIsrayeli, ozanikela umnikelo wakhe ngezithembiso zabo zonke, langokweminikelo yabo yonke yesihle, abazayinikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 1.2,3,10. Nani 15.14.\x*,
\v 19 ukuze lemukeleke, iduna elingelasici, elezinkomo, elezimvu, loba elembuzi\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 20 Linganikeli loba ngakuphi okulesici kukho, ngoba kakuyikwemukeleka kini\x + Dute. 15.21; 17.1. Mal. 1.8,14; Heb. 9.14. 1 Pet. 1.19.\x*.
\v 21 Umuntu, nxa enikela-ke umhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 3.1,6; 7.16.\x* wesithembiso esikhethekileyo loba womnikelo wesihle, enkomeni loba ezimvini, kumele uphelele ukuze wemukeleke, kungabi lasici kuwo\x + Nani 15.3,8. Dute. 23.21,23. Hlab. 61.8. 65.1. Tshu. 5.4,5.\x*.
\v 22 Eziyiziphofu, kumbe ezephukileyo, kumbe eziyizilima, kumbe ezilensumpa\x + 22.20. Mal. 1.8.\x*, kumbe eziloqweqwe, kumbe ezilamathumba\x + 21.20.\x*, linganikeli lezi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, futhi linganikeli kulezi umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni phezu kwelathi\x + 1.9,13; 3.3,5.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa inkunzi loba imvu elesitho eselulekileyo kumbe esidundubeleyo lingayinikela ibe ngumnikelo wesihle; kodwa kayiyikwemukeleka ukuba ngeyesithembiso\x + 21.18.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo linganikeli eN\nd kosi\nd*ni okuhluzukileyo kumbe okugxotshiweyo loba okudatshuliweyo loba okuqunyiweyo; lingakwenzi elizweni lakini.
\v 25 Ngokuvela esandleni sowemzini linganikeli isinkwa sikaNkulunkulu wenu okuvela kuzo zonke lezi\x + 3.11.\x*; ngoba ukonakala kwazo kukuzo, isici sikuzo, kaziyikwemukeleka kini\x + Mal. 1.14.\x*.
\p
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 27 Nxa kuzalwa inkunzi loba imvu loba imbuzi, izakuba ngaphansi kukanina insuku eziyisikhombisa. Njalo kusukela kusuku lwesificaminwembili njalo kusiya phambili izakwemukeleka ibe ngumnikelo, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo\x + Eks. 22.30.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa inkomokazi loba imvukazi lingayihlabi lomntwana wayo ngasuku lunye\x + Dute. 22.6.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo nxa lihlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* umhlatshelo wokubonga, lizawuhlaba ukuze lemukeleke\x + 7.12. Hlab. 107.22. 116.17.\x*.
\v 30 Uzadliwa ngalolosuku, lingatshiyi okwawo kuze kube sekuseni. NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + 7.15.\x*\nd*.
\v 31 Ngakho gcinani imilayo yami, liyenze. NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + 19.37. Nani 15.40. Dute. 4.40.\x*\nd*.
\v 32 Njalo lingeyisi ibizo lami elingcwele\x + 22.18,21.\x*, kodwa ngizangcweliswa phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli. NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + 10.3.\x*\nd* elingcwelisayo\x + 20.8.\x*,
\v 33 eyalikhupha elizweni leGibhithe ukuze ngibe nguNkulunkulu wenu. NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 6.7; Levi 11.45; 19.36; 25.38,42,55; 26.45. Nani 15.41.\x*\nd*.